            <title>[WICKET-3361] Validation Error on AjaxEditableLabel causes ajax calls in loop on Chrome Browser</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-3361</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On Chrome, the component AjaxEditableLabel causes an infinite ajax call&apos;s loop if there is an validation error on the input.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The attached project shows this bug (Enter &quot;false&quot; to reproduce the bug, and tape any key to stop it).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On Firefox, everithing is OK.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
